<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brewer" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brewer,</orth> one who makes beer: <cit><quote>a --'s horse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he that gibbets on the --'s bucket,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.282" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 282</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--s mar their malt with water,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 2, 82</bibl></cit>.
